    <p id="footnote_2">[2] This reminds me of a somewhat amusing anecdote I thought fitting to share here. A while ago, whilst talking to one of my colleagues at work, the topic of beer was brought up in our conversation. What exactly prompted this I do not remember, but I distinctly remember his saying that Germans had invented beer. I remarked, thereupon, that even the Ancient Egyptians enjoyed their own version of a pint, he was struck with disbelief and proclaimed that surely their <q>beer</q> cannot have been real beer at all — for it was us, the Germans, who have invented it! This was followed by my slowly nodding in fake agreement to move the conversation further. <a href="#footnote_2_ref">Back to text</a></p>
  </div>
